{"tid":909240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IG驚見「自己的複製人」　詭異女子活在平行時空照抄2年","createTime":"2018-11-20T08:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T02:52:37.000Z","uid":28765,"like":451,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"9e789fd8ffe4ae6bc3cc5df1395d4d77f7984f83","tid":909240,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3707/d3707664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3707%2Fd3707664.jpg&h=4f2201e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲克洛伊（圖左）比對自己與另一名女子的照片，發現許多雷同之處。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n英國蘇格蘭丹地女學生克洛伊（Chloe Cowan）喜歡經營社群媒體Instagram，但她近期卻發現，有另外一名女子默默複製她的風格長達2年，兩人的照片與貼文幾乎完全相同，對方還會模仿她的姿勢，在類似的景點打卡。克洛伊的手足琳芝（Linzi Cowan）相當驚嚇，透過臉書呼籲大家應注意社群媒體上隱藏的危險。<br />\n《每日郵報》報導，蘇格蘭警方表示，還無法確定在當地是否有接獲相關報案，也不能明白這位IG用戶的動機為何。克洛伊經常透過網路與好友分享自己的生活，她穿著黑色洋裝，戴上圓眼鏡並拄著拐杖，有時則換成比基尼在湖畔邊打卡。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到，有另一名女子完全複製克洛伊的風格，經過比對，兩人的貼文看起來十分相似，甚至她還會模仿克洛伊的神情與動作，有時直接貼上沒修改過的文字，宛如複製人。讓琳芝感到恐懼的是，當克洛伊製作短片給已過世的父親時，不知名的女子甚至照抄這樣的舉動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://external.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQDZeJrTXCYU9xBU&amp;w=540&amp;h=282&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F11%2F19%2F15%2F6385888-0-image-a-119_1542643028829.jpg&amp;cfs=1&amp;upscale=1&amp;fallback=news_d_placeholder_publisher&amp;_nc_hash=AQAS4hFuEE5x0HDB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQDZeJrTXCYU9xBU%26w%3D540%26h%3D282%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fi.dailymail.co.uk%252F1s%252F2018%252F11%252F19%252F15%252F6385888-0-image-a-119_1542643028829.jpg%26cfs%3D1%26upscale%3D1%26fallback%3Dnews_d_placeholder_publisher%26_nc_hash%3DAQAS4hFuEE5x0HDB&h=e9217cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://external.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQDWyL8KY1O00VKI&amp;w=540&amp;h=282&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.dailyrecord.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle13614595.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs1200%2F0_JS168864104.jpg&amp;cfs=1&amp;upscale=1&amp;fallback=news_d_placeholder_publisher&amp;_nc_hash=AQCMRooznpJwaiMS\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQDWyL8KY1O00VKI%26w%3D540%26h%3D282%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fi2-prod.dailyrecord.co.uk%252Fincoming%252Farticle13614595.ece%252FALTERNATES%252Fs1200%252F0_JS168864104.jpg%26cfs%3D1%26upscale%3D1%26fallback%3Dnews_d_placeholder_publisher%26_nc_hash%3DAQCMRooznpJwaiMS&h=51f47330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原文網址: 她在IG驚見「自己的複製人」　詭異女子活在平行時空照抄2年 | ETtoday國際 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181120/1310908.htm#ixzz5XNlO66cC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181120%2F1310908.htm%23ixzz5XNlO66cC&d=Q2fpNZjU8e7BPMXOjrwcQcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ad2fb687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181120/1310908.htm#ixzz5XNlO66cC</a>"},{"pid":"46a572e0c802a0633fdc27071bfb25ca035ec0df","tid":909240,"uid":56240,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"陰謀黎"},{"pid":"bd84bf568ce9f2fe29ef145c05f8a419fd1d6071","tid":909240,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a4555f76280735824afa65622f40a211655c6a","tid":909240,"uid":73613,"like":533,"dislike":2,"score":531,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67ca3a03145c2c89aa39d61fc172ca7282094731","tid":909240,"uid":156376,"like":174,"dislike":49,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"複製人靚過原身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49dfb133d3b8495f4b7bdf89039469cf16daf54a","tid":909240,"uid":193192,"like":712,"dislike":14,"score":698,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so